{"tid":535896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佳士得辦公室貼007海報","createTime":"2018-01-21T10:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T12:22:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d53f1c2e8dfc59215dc967c6497e651578edca","tid":535896,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180121/20281008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F20281008&d=3uCXtnqEHcYCu2otEXs5XgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=f020cd6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F20281008&h=49cb38d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180121/20281008</a><br />\n<br />\n佳士得辦公室貼007海報<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180121/large/a0202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180121%2Flarge%2Fa0202a.gif&h=4576349a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李的辦公室貼有與上圖類似的占士邦海報。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美諜變主角、港產CIA前特工李振成在香港的辦公室陳設曝光。有消息指，李振成被捕前在本港著名國際拍賣行佳士得出任亞洲區保安主管。經常出差到中國內地及東南亞地區；他的辦公室貼有一張荷李活影星辛康納利版的英國特務占士邦007電影海報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屢到中國出差<br />\n<br />\n率先披露港產前CIA特工李振成照片的本港藝術新聞平台The Value相信，該張海報屬於佳士得1998年一場007專場拍賣會，當時共有270件拍賣品，大部份為電影道具，來自《鐵金剛勇破雪山堡》（On Her Majesty's Secret Service）、《新鐵金剛之金眼睛》（Golden Eye）、《鐵金剛勇破海底城》（The Spy Who Loved Me）等007電影。<br />\n《蘋果》記者翻查佳士得網站，發現佳士得當年9月曾經在倫敦舉行007電影拍賣會，當中包括多張辛康納利的電影海報。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息稱，李振成在紐約被FBI拘捕後，佳士得立即封鎖了他在香港的辦公房間，員工也無法再在公司電腦系統中找到相關資料。<br />\n<br />\n據報，李振成2016年6月出任佳士得亞洲區保安主管，因工作關係，經常離港出差，前往中國、東南亞等地，主要負責護送藝術品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t被指助中國破解美通訊系統　令機密外洩港產CIA前特工　涉害死在俄美諜<br />\n要聞 5小時前"},{"pid":"0ad78508e3e899d6d4617c68c298a8b3e719739c","tid":535896,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27c44ff9e3b294e77bed8795107c30baed14d5a","tid":535896,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"貼Bourne Identity好過啦"},{"pid":"9e8a1042ad514b84a12c53a993e37374b390632a","tid":535896,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27c44ff9e3b294e77bed8795107c30baed14d5a","tid":535896,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"貼Bourne Identity好過啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"佢個輩應睇007大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65676c24a606952f4cdf7f15232a138f4e9dafcb","tid":535896,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"貼周星馳好過啦<br />\n國家終於有任務俾你喇呀柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b32e81ced3bb6befed0d5cd8c96ba1625123783","tid":535896,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e8a1042ad514b84a12c53a993e37374b390632a","tid":535896,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27c44ff9e3b294e77bed8795107c30baed14d5a","tid":535896,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"貼Bourne Identity好過啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"佢個輩應睇007大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"六十年代以嚟，好似無咩邊代細個無睇過007<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets